# service_role key (NOT anon) — bypasses RLS, keep secret.
# Throwaway POC project, so low-stakes; still don't commit it.
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=

# T7: rag_api(FastAPI) 공유 토큰 — Activepieces HTTP 헤더 X-API-Token 과 비교. 임의 난수 문자열.
